1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:04,800
Science has a clearer story about histone acetylation than social media does.

2
00:00:04,800 --> 00:00:10,800
Histone acetylation is a process that modifies proteins called histones, influencing how our genes express.

3
00:00:10,800 --> 00:00:15,200
When histones are acetylated, DNA becomes more accessible, turning genes on.

4
00:00:15,200 --> 00:00:21,200
Studies show that this process plays a critical role in development and diseases like cancer.

5
00:00:21,200 --> 00:00:24,800
Understanding histone acetylation could unlock new treatments and therapies.

6
00:00:24,800 --> 00:00:28,400
